"First Im going to kiss
him,then Im going to kill him."

65
00:05:26,020 --> 00:05:31,450
Transcripts of your conversations with
strangers,in various drinking dens,

66
00:05:31,460 --> 00:05:35,120
since you first came to our attention.

67
