Yknow,no-one
likes a smart-ass.

68
00:05:37,330 --> 00:05:39,850
Tell us where he is
and well release you.

69
00:05:39,860 --> 00:05:40,460
Why do you wanna know?

70
00:05:40,470 --> 00:05:43,110
Youre in Torchwood,Cardiff.

71
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:48,300
The Torchwood Institute was created to
combat the threat posed by the Doctor

72
00:05:48,310 --> 00:05:51,410
and other phantasmagoria.

73
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,280
Hes not a threat.

74
00:05:54,290 --> 00:05:58,970
The Doctors the one wholl save
you from your phantasmahoojits.

75
00:05:58,980 --> 00:06:00,210
Just tell us his location.

76
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:02,560
I dont know!

77
00:06:05,010 --> 00:06:06,940
He left me behind.

78
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:09,660
I came here to find him.

79
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:14,290
He refuels from that rift you have.

80
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:18,430
Hoping if I stayed here long
enough,wed find each other.

81
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:22,670
Now,can I go?

82
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,430
No.

83
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,300
You cant keep me here!

84
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:26,730
Oh,we can.

85
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:29,170
- Unless...
- Yes.

86
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:30,450
Unless.

87
00:06:30,460 --> 00:06:31,360
Unless what?

88
00:06:31,370 --> 00:06:33,010
There are opportunities here.

89
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:34,430
With the Institute.

90
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:35,400
Im not for hire.

91
00:06:35,410 --> 00:06:38,320
Youre going to need currency.

92
00:06:41,490 --> 00:06:42,390
Whats the assignment?

93
